Full Implementation Plan: Smart Attendance Management System
A robust, role-based system for automating attendance, explicitly designed to satisfy the SEM III Python-1 & FSD-1 syllabus.

üöÄ Tech Stack
Backend: Flask (Python)
Database: Pure PostgreSQL (using Raw SQL via psycopg2)
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3 (Vanilla + Bootstrap 5), JS (ES6)
Reporting: ReportLab / WeasyPrint
Analytics: Matplotlib (Visualization), Custom BST (Data Structures)
Frontend Responsibilities (FSD-1 Alignment)
Responsive dashboards using Bootstrap 5.
Dynamic attendance updates via JS (ES6 + AJAX/Fetch).
Real-time filters and Matplotlib chart integration.
Comprehensive client-side validation.

